    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification registers a kind of URI that represents a JSON Web Key (JWK) Thumbprint value.  JWK Thumbprints are defined in RFC 7638.  This enables JWK Thumbprints to be used, for instance, as key identifiers in contexts requiring URIs.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
